-- v1.1+ per clarify Q1. v1.0 ships solid sides + solid windshield face.

deferred Railings.stanchion_and_rail
-- Discrete stanchion + rail railings deferred to v1.1+. v1.0 ships continuous
-- perimeter rail loops only.

deferred Deck.fly_bridge
deferred Deck.swim_platform
deferred Deck.anchor_pulpit
deferred Deck.transom_door
-- All non-core superstructure elements deferred to v1.1+ or downstream specs.
